<br>
If you fall through a hole, even by accident, then you have done the same and are a &quot;cheater&quot;. What do you do about it?<br>
<br>
Lots of people have reported these holes and Mythic have not repaired them. This means that you can fall through by &quot;by acciddent&quot; still.<br>
<br>
Yes, it is an exploit, but it is there for 2 reasons.<br>
<br>
1. BAD CODING<br>
2. LOW FIX PRIORITY<br>
<br>
If it is a low fix priority, then the bug/exploit is considered minor. BUT remember, some bugs end up as intentional code, so lets presume that its not been fixed because Mythic will make it intentional.<br>
